    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is ready to go and super reliable. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it still drives like a total dream. Come take it for a spin\u2014I just know you're going to love it!",
