    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable daily driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, with only very minor stone chips and light surface scratches that are typical for its age. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive shape; the leather seats are soft and free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Every button, from the heated seats to the premium infotainment system, operates perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a consistent service history. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It is a clean, smoke-free vehicle that drives as well as it looks, offering a refined experience for its next owner.",
